Reading: the Kalman ADF passes BOTH groups at ~the same high rate (no discrimination; its innovations
are white in both), while the clean EG/static tests pass the positive control and stay near the null
floor on the negatives. So the Kalman screen carries ~zero cointegration information; the clean tests carry it.
